snippet.title: Underquest - Roguelite Backpack Autobattler - Demo Trailer
snippet.description:
⚔️ Cute fantasy roguelite with backpack mechanics. Combine items to create powerful skills and use them in fast-paced combat. Explore randomly generated dungeons in the Underkingdom and discover the secrets of its inhabitants!

Add game to wishlist on Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2265420/Underquest/
